caption.center: PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. TAVARIOUS ARNELL

opinion.opinion_text:
SC: 128722, COA: 253246, Oakland CC: 03-188275-FH.
On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the April 14, 2005 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
